==English==
===Etymology===
Shortened from '''[[Pakistani]]'''

===Proper noun===
'''Paki''' (''plural'' '''Pakis''')

#(''derogatory, offensive and racist'') A [[Pakistani]], or, more generally, a person of who is perceived to be a Pakistani; often applied to persons of any South Asian or Middle Eastern origin - or indeed any immigrant.


